dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Roads_2017.gdb. [The roads layer depicts road centerlines and address ranges for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data was created to cartographically inform citizens as well as public and private officials of the location of roads in Fond du Lac County. ]
